{"title":"西财摄记｜忽而今夏","uid":"7269716cb17cff2efbecc9bd1aa4ae5a","slug":"推文5","date":"2021-07-19T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T15:22:42.756Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文5.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303225943513.png","content":"<p>序</p>\n<p>你是一种感觉，</p>\n<p>写在夏日晚风里。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303225925158.png\" alt=\"image-20220303225925158\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"盛夏的光\"><a href=\"#盛夏的光\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"盛夏的光\"></a>盛夏的光</h2><p>夏天的光，为成都增添了许多浪漫气息。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303225943513.png\" alt=\"image-20220303225943513\"></p>\n<p>和许多人一样，我在上课途中，也常常流连于难得一见的蓝天白云。 </p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303225955246.png\" alt=\"image-20220303225955246\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303225959746.png\" alt=\"image-20220303225959746\"></p>\n<p>一直想拍一组宫崎骏夏天味道的写真，可惜校内没有十分合适的地点。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230008707.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230008707\"></p>\n<p>想起平常散步经常去的鲁家滩，清凉又治愈。挑了个阳光明媚的下午，就和静宝一块儿过</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230017946.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230017946\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230022413.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230022413\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"夏天的风\"><a href=\"#夏天的风\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"夏天的风\"></a>夏天的风</h2><p>蓝天、白云、绿树、小溪、西瓜。</p>\n<p>夏天的事物一应俱全。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230036137.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230036137\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230039297.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230039297\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230043315.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230043315\"></p>\n<p>站在台阶上，向上望去，我们都惊讶于在成都好久没看见这么大片云朵了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230051060.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230051060\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230055522.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230055522\"></p>\n<p>微风吹拂，少女的跳跃与白色裙摆，在蓝天白云的衬托下治愈人心。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230104840.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230104840\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230107506.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230107506\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230113786.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230113786\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"清凉一夏\"><a href=\"#清凉一夏\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"清凉一夏\"></a>清凉一夏</h2><p>拍摄途中，偶然间我们发现了一处溪流。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230129601.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230129601\"></p>\n<p>潺潺的小溪，旁边有孩童在玩闹，油油的水草，摆动着柔媚的线条。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230137198.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230137198\"></p>\n<p>有那么恍惚的一刹那，我的记忆被拉回了童年的夏天。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230147371.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230147371\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230154160.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230154160\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"终语\"><a href=\"#终语\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"终语\"></a>终语</h2><p>渐渐的，日落西山。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230206953.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230206953\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230210215.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230210215\"></p>\n<p>和静宝的这次拍摄也在欢声笑语中结束了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230220609.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230220609\"></p>\n<p>但有关夏天的故事，才刚刚开始。</p>\n<p>![image-20220303230230071](/Users/yuhangxue/Library/Application Support/typora-user-images/image-20220303230230071.png)</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230311343.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230311343\"></p>\n<p>:::detail 感谢</p>\n<p>文|李宜霏</p>\n<p>排版|刘雨童</p>\n<p>摄|李宜霏、刘雨童</p>\n<p>出镜|邓静</p>\n<p>:::</p>\n","text":"序 你是一种感觉， 写在夏日晚风里。 盛夏的光夏天的光，为成都增添了许多浪漫气息。 和许多人一样，我在上课途中，也常常流连于难得一见的蓝天白云。 一直想拍一组宫崎骏夏天味道的写真，可惜校内没有十分合适的地点。 想起平常散步经常去的鲁家滩，清凉又治愈。挑了个阳光明媚的下午，就和静宝...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":558,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"夏","slug":"夏","count":6,"path":"api/tags/夏.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%9B%9B%E5%A4%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%85%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">盛夏的光</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%84%E9%A3%8E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">夏天的风</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B8%85%E5%87%89%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">清凉一夏</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BB%88%E8%AF%AD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">终语</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Swufe了吗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/deelsilcon/pics/raw/master/uPic/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"分享生活，记录美好","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"weichat":{"icon":"/img/wechat.png","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/profile_ext?action=home&__biz=Mzg3MTU3NDkwNA==&scene=124#wechat_redirect"},"mail":{"icon":"/img/mail.png","link":"mailto:271215314@qq.com"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"西财摄记 | 整个夏天想和你环游世界","uid":"a93e87b2f48eb84fe192d269e2ab9b32","slug":"推文7","date":"20